NK081(zhu)001:1: // s+th+aa n+aa ga ma ka la sho da sh+aam n+aa m+aa s+su bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK081(zhu)001:2: gnas kyi lung phran bcu drug ces bya ba rnams legs par bzhugs so //
NK081(zhu)001:4: gnas kyi gzhung dal bstan pa'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:5: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor rgyan gyi lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:6: dkyil 'khor pho brang bum pa'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:7: tshe 'das rnam shes dgug pa'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:8: rnam shes dgug pa'i gtan tshigs lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:9: gshin bla 'gugs pa man ngag lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:10: thugs rje chen pos sbyang ba'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:11: thabs dang shes rab mda' gzhu'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:12: gnas kyi sa dang lam gyi lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:13: h'u nyid ring por spar ba'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:14: bcol dang bskang bar bya ba'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:15: dge ba'i bshes gnyen mnga' dbul lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:16: tshe 'das rnam rtog gri 'dul lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:17: sbub 'jug bshig pa sri 'dul lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:18: gdos bcas bsreg sbyang mi yi lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:19: mchod rten gdab pa'i rus chog lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:20: sgyu lus rang sar grol ba'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:21: gzungs ma rang bzhin khug pa'i lung phran dang //
NK081(zhu)001:23: gzhug ma gnyis bod la bstan pa'i snod med par slar rgya gar du bsnams so //
NK081(zhu)001:24: lung phran zhes bya ba ni /
NK081(zhu)001:25: bka'i don sgro skur dang bral ba'i lung cha shas ston pas na phran zhes bya'o //
NK081(zhu)001:26: lung phran bco brgyad pa'i sdom tshig rdzogs so ////gnas kyi gzhung dkyil bstan pa'i lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:28: b+h+r+aum a nu tan+t+ra hri ta pany+tsa n+aa ma /
NK081(zhu)001:30: gnas lung rgyud kyi snying po bsdus pa zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:31: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das zhi khro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:32: 'di skad lung du bstan pa'i dus gcig na /
NK081(zhu)001:33: bcom ldan 'das steng gi phyogs na thams cad sgrol ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK081(zhu)001:34: dkyil 'khor drug ma 'ongs pa'i don phyi ma dang bdun /
NK081(zhu)001:35: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas phyungs te //
NK081(zhu)001:36: ma lus par byin gyis brlabs par mdzad do //
NK081(zhu)001:37: dang po brtag pa'i gnas chen du //
NK081(zhu)001:38: sngags mkhan bya ba kun byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:39: khro bo mang po bkram nas ni //
NK081(zhu)001:40: bgegs rnams rdul du rlog bzhin byer //
NK081(zhu)001:41: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa tshul bzhin bzhag /bum pa byin rlabs bzang mos brgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:42: ma nor lha ni bsnyen byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:43: cha med sangs rgyas kun la zhu //
NK081(zhu)001:44: byin dbab gsal bar rdzogs nas ni //
NK081(zhu)001:45: phyogs skyod lan chags gtang bar bya //
NK081(zhu)001:46: rgyud lnga'i lam nas drag pos bsgral //
NK081(zhu)001:47: gsal ba'i thugs rje sems la gzung //
NK081(zhu)001:48: tsit+ta la ni lhan ne bos //
NK081(zhu)001:49: thabs dang shes rab ma g.yos pa'i //
NK081(zhu)001:50: gru gsum par ni bsgral bar bya //
NK081(zhu)001:51: bcas te sngags dang phyag rgya yis //
NK081(zhu)001:52: yab yum gnas su phata kyis 'phang //
NK081(zhu)001:53: bo de tsit+tasa dbang bskur te //
NK081(zhu)001:54: lhag ma bshags sbyangs sman bcos bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:55: h'u mdzad kyi rgyud chen po las /
NK081(zhu)001:56: ma h+aa rak+ta ga na yi le'u rno ngar gyi
NK081(zhu)001:57: gnas kyi lung nyi tshe zhig /a tsarma gu ru
NK081(zhu)001:58: rdo rje gro bo lod dang lots+tsha ba rdo rje
NK081(zhu)001:59: zhang drung gis bsgyur te gtan la phab pa'o ////gzugs
NK081(zhu)001:60: brnyan dkyil 'khor rgyan gyi lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:62: ru pa man+dala la a lam ka ra a ti
NK081(zhu)001:63: ka rak+sha da ka n+aa dri med zla nan ma
NK081(zhu)001:65: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor rgyan gyi lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:66: bcom ldan sgrol byed rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:67: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sel byed cing //
NK081(zhu)001:68: thar pa'i lam mchog mngon 'thob byed //
NK081(zhu)001:69: dkyil 'khor cho ga gsungs pa las //
NK081(zhu)001:70: rgyan dgod yo ga gnyis dgod bstan //
NK081(zhu)001:71: dkyil 'khor la sogs gzugs brnyan gyi //
NK081(zhu)001:72: rgyan la don rtags gnyis su shes //
NK081(zhu)001:73: don ni gnyis med snang stong la //
NK081(zhu)001:74: dkor bdun lhun grub rang snang brgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:75: gos la gnas dang gang zag dang //
NK081(zhu)001:77: dang po khang bzang byi dor bya //
NK081(zhu)001:78: steng rgyan 'phan gdugs bla re bres //
NK081(zhu)001:79: ba dan lhab lhub phye phur dang //
NK081(zhu)001:80: rin chen lha mos bar snang brgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:81: logs rgyan rgyab yol za ra tshags //
NK081(zhu)001:82: khri gdan mchod cha 'og gi rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:83: byin can sku gzugs thang sku dgram //
NK081(zhu)001:84: gang zag sgrub pa po yi rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:85: stod g.yogs smad dkris thugs khebs sogs //
NK081(zhu)001:86: rgyan cha bcu gsum gyis brgyan bya //
NK081(zhu)001:87: thams cad dngos po bzang zhing mdzes //
NK081(zhu)001:88: gsang zhing byin gyis brlab par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:89: yang na khro bo'i cha byad dgod //
NK081(zhu)001:90: man+dala las rnams bya ba ni //
NK081(zhu)001:91: brtsegs steng zhal zhal chag chag gdab //
NK081(zhu)001:92: thig tshon gzhung bzhin legs bris la //
NK081(zhu)001:93: rnam pa 'chod dang rgyan dgod pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:94: khro bo yongs rdzogs sku rnams dang //
NK081(zhu)001:95: yang na thugs kyi phyag mtshan dgod //
NK081(zhu)001:96: bsdu na yig 'bru bri bar bya //
NK081(zhu)001:97: ma nor rang dang gnas su'o //
NK081(zhu)001:98: rgyan la steng rgyan lding bu ni //
NK081(zhu)001:99: ye shes bla ma mtshon ma'i phyir //
NK081(zhu)001:100: mthing ga a mtshon steng nas dgab //
NK081(zhu)001:101: 'khor lo tshogs chen sa mtshon pa'i //
NK081(zhu)001:102: zhi ba thugs rje'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:103: ma chags pad spyan dmar po yis //
NK081(zhu)001:104: gzugs brnyan dkyil dkyil 'gebs pa'i tshul //
NK081(zhu)001:105: dkyil 'khor rnams gnyis dbyer med phyir //
NK081(zhu)001:106: bum pa rgyan rnams rab gnas rdzogs //
NK081(zhu)001:107: zhi khro byin can dbus su'o //
NK081(zhu)001:108: mtha' skor logs kyi rgyan pa ni //
NK081(zhu)001:109: rang bzhin dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK081(zhu)001:110: mtshan ldan b+han+d+ha bzang po brgyad //
NK081(zhu)001:111: sman 'bru rat+nasa bkang la bzhag /bar chad mi tshugs mtshams gcod rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:112: khro bcu bskyed pa'i phur pa bcu //
NK081(zhu)001:113: phyogs mtshams steng 'og bcu ru gdab //
NK081(zhu)001:114: 'jig rten gtso bo gus pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:115: mda' brgyad lha chen brgyad du bskyed //
NK081(zhu)001:116: phyogs mtshams brgyad du drang por gzugs //
NK081(zhu)001:117: ye shes lnga yis kun khyab rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:118: rigs lnga mtshon pa'i skud pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:119: steng 'og kha khyer ris su bres //
NK081(zhu)001:120: mchod sprin rgyun mi 'chad pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:121: gzugs sogs lha mor bsgoms pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:122: dar sna brgyad kyang gdab par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:123: don gsal bde ba bskyed pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:124: nang gsal lha mor gsal ba yi //
NK081(zhu)001:125: me long brgyad kyang gong bzhin no //
NK081(zhu)001:126: 'dod yon lhun gyis grub pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:127: rin chen sna bdun gter bum pa //
NK081(zhu)001:128: brgyad kyis mtha' ma bskor ba yin //
NK081(zhu)001:129: thun mong yon tan kun rdzogs rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:130: sngon tshe rgyal ba las byung ba'i //
NK081(zhu)001:131: bkra shis rtags brgyad dgram par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:132: mi nub 'gro don mdzad pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:133: dom dang seng ge stag dang gzig /rgyal mtshan bzhi ni phyogs bzhir bslang //
NK081(zhu)001:134: chos skyong mkha' 'gro dgyes pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:135: dkar khra ser khra dmar khra dang //
NK081(zhu)001:136: sngo khra dar bzhi mtshams bzhir phyar //
NK081(zhu)001:137: srid pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:138: sgo bzhir khro bo bskyed pa yi //
NK081(zhu)001:139: ral gri bzhi yang phyogs bzhi ste //
NK081(zhu)001:140: ma rig mun pa sel ba'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:141: kun snang gsal ba'i mar me brgyad //
NK081(zhu)001:142: dkyil 'khor mtha' nas bkod par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:143: khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:144: phyogs skyong rgyal chen bcu bzhi yang //
NK081(zhu)001:145: mtha' nas bskor zhing gus par gsal //
NK081(zhu)001:146: de dag thun mong rgyan zhes bya //
NK081(zhu)001:147: khyad par dur khrod brgyad kyi rgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:148: gnas brgyad shing dang zhing skyong dang //
NK081(zhu)001:149: phyogs skyong rnal 'byor mtsho dang sprin //
NK081(zhu)001:150: klu brgyad de dag la sogs su //
NK081(zhu)001:151: sha za srin po gshin rje dang //
NK081(zhu)001:152: mkha' 'gro bya khyi ro langs sogs //
NK081(zhu)001:153: ce spyang khros pa'i sgra 'byin cing //
NK081(zhu)001:154: ro yi tshogs la longs spyod mdzad //
NK081(zhu)001:155: rang byung mtsho chen dang bcas pa //
NK081(zhu)001:156: phreng ba rim gsum phyi rol gnas //
NK081(zhu)001:157: kun 'byung brgyad kyis mtshams spras te //
NK081(zhu)001:158: dpag bsam rin chen ljon shing dang //
NK081(zhu)001:160: rin chen sa gzhi khrus kyi rdzing //
NK081(zhu)001:161: yid bzhin bsam 'phel nor bu dang //
NK081(zhu)001:162: 'bru tshogs zhing kun mdzes par brgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:163: bla med rgyan ni zhing chen bla re dang //
NK081(zhu)001:164: zhing gi rgyal mtshan zhing phran 'phan gdugs dang //
NK081(zhu)001:165: dkyil 'khor legs rnams keng rus ri rab dang //
NK081(zhu)001:166: rak+ta'i mtsho dang zhing chen lang ling dang //
NK081(zhu)001:167: rgyu ma'i d+r+wa phyed tsit+ta'i phreng ba'o //
NK081(zhu)001:168: thod pa skam rlon la sogs bsam yas pa //
NK081(zhu)001:169: rgyud nas bshad pa bzhin du 'dir bsgrub bya //
NK081(zhu)001:170: mchod pa'i rgyan la phyi nang gsang gsum ste //
NK081(zhu)001:171: rang bzhin dag pa'i pu tsa rnam pa bdun //
NK081(zhu)001:172: zhabs bsil chu gtsang tsan+dana sbyar ba dang //
NK081(zhu)001:173: chu skyes thang skyes yid 'ong me tog dang //
NK081(zhu)001:174: lhan skyes sbyar byung bdug spos du ma dang //
NK081(zhu)001:175: byug pa chu gtsang dkar gsum sman snas bran //
NK081(zhu)001:176: zhal zas lha bshos ro mchog phun sum tshogs //
NK081(zhu)001:177: snang gsal 'bru mar zhun mar khu ba'i me //
NK081(zhu)001:178: cha lang gling bu sgra snyan sna tshogs bshams //
NK081(zhu)001:179: nang gi pu tsa 'dod yon rnam lngas te //
NK081(zhu)001:180: gzugs mdzes me long la sogs mang po dang //
NK081(zhu)001:181: sgra snyan zin dang ma zin mang po dang //
NK081(zhu)001:182: dri zhim tshim byed spos mchog sna tshogs dang //
NK081(zhu)001:183: ro bcud ldan pa'i zhal zas bsam yas dang //
NK081(zhu)001:184: reg bya 'jam zhing bde ba ma lus bshams //
NK081(zhu)001:185: gsang ba'i mchod pa ma lus thams cad kun //
NK081(zhu)001:186: khyad par rmad du byung ba'i mchod pa ste //
NK081(zhu)001:187: dam rdzas ldan pa'i dpal gtor chen po dang //
NK081(zhu)001:188: 'bru bcud bzhi bcas rtsa brgyad stong sbyar sman //
NK081(zhu)001:189: m+aam sar bcas pa'i rak+ta chen po dang //
NK081(zhu)001:190: srung ma mchod pa'i dkar gtor dmar gtor dang //
NK081(zhu)001:191: mtshan ldan gzungs ma khrus dbyung rgyan cha bstar //
NK081(zhu)001:192: bskang ba'i rdzas la bya lug shel sgong dang //
NK081(zhu)001:193: 'jig rten longs spyod ru tshad 'dir bsdu'o /
NK081(zhu)001:194: bdag don dngos grub sgrub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK081(zhu)001:195: gzhan don dbang dang rab gnas kun la gces //
NK081(zhu)001:196: mi snang gshin po'i cho ga 'dir bstan yin //
NK081(zhu)001:197: phrin las gang sgrub rdzas rnams rang gzhung ltos //
NK081(zhu)001:198: 'di ni spyi yi gdams pa thob tsam yin //
NK081(zhu)001:199: bstan pa'i don 'di rgyun du bkod tsam gyis //
NK081(zhu)001:200: bde gshegs rgyal ba kun kyang mnyes gyur te //
NK081(zhu)001:201: rig 'dzin byang sems rnams kyis byin rlob 'gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:202: mkha' 'gro chos skyong phrin las myur 'grub la //
NK081(zhu)001:203: 'jig rten gtso dang 'khor gyis bskor bar byed //
NK081(zhu)001:204: dbang sgrub dbang byed rdo rje 'chang par sgrol //
NK081(zhu)001:205: dge bas snang dang mi snang don yod shog /gzugs
NK081(zhu)001:206: brnyan dkyil 'khor rgyan gyi lung phran zhes bya ba
NK081(zhu)001:207: rdzogs so // rgya gar gyi mkhan po bi ma la mi tra dang //
NK081(zhu)001:208: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ras
NK081(zhu)001:209: bsgyur ba'o ////dkyil 'khor pho brang bum pa'i lung phran
NK081(zhu)001:210: / ye shes rang gnas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:211: gnas lung rgyud du gsungs pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:212: bum pa byin rlabs bzang mos brgyan //
NK081(zhu)001:213: mdo tsam bsdus te bstan par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:214: nges tshig bsham lugs byin rlabs te //
NK081(zhu)001:215: rab gnas gzhugs su gsol ba yis //
NK081(zhu)001:216: bum pa'i cho ga shes par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:217: dang po phyi nang rnam pa gnyis //
NK081(zhu)001:218: phyi yang shes rab yum gyi dbyings //
NK081(zhu)001:219: lam lnga bgrod cing dbyings su phyin //
NK081(zhu)001:220: byang chub chos rnams yongs su rdzogs //
NK081(zhu)001:221: rang nyid lha dang yab kyi tshul //
NK081(zhu)001:222: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pas //
NK081(zhu)001:223: byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun gyis //
NK081(zhu)001:224: gzung 'dzin dag cing sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK081(zhu)001:225: byang sems dbang gi da la yang //
NK081(zhu)001:226: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du rdzogs //
NK081(zhu)001:227: rin chen lnga'am kham sa la //
NK081(zhu)001:228: lto dang mgrin pa tshad ldan zhing //
NK081(zhu)001:229: gur gum rgya spos dri zhim pas //
NK081(zhu)001:230: sngags bzlas shin tu dag par bkru //
NK081(zhu)001:231: bdud 'khyil yab lnga'i sngags bzlas shing //
NK081(zhu)001:232: gu gul la sogs dud pas bdug /dkar zhal btang ste yum bzhi yi //
NK081(zhu)001:233: phyag rgya'am snying po'i sngags rnams bri //
NK081(zhu)001:234: cha rkyen chu dang 'o ma dang //
NK081(zhu)001:235: dri lnga sman lnga spos lnga dang //
NK081(zhu)001:236: rin chen lnga dang 'bru lnga dang //
NK081(zhu)001:237: snying po lnga dang kha rgyan bcas //
NK081(zhu)001:238: dar ras la sogs mgul chings dang //
NK081(zhu)001:239: rin chen brgyus pa'i gzungs thag bshams //
NK081(zhu)001:240: dri ma bzung zhing brkyang phyag dang //
NK081(zhu)001:241: lha bskyed gsang brlab bden pa bdar //
NK081(zhu)001:242: sprul bkye bar du gcod pa srungs //
NK081(zhu)001:243: bdud 'khyil sngags bzlas dud pas bdug /phyag g.yon 'khyud cing g.yas pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:244: gus pas bum pa'i kha bkag ste //
NK081(zhu)001:245: yum gyi sngags bzlas zab mo'i mkha' //thugs nas b+h+r+aum bton sngags bzlas pas //
NK081(zhu)001:246: 'khor lo zlum po rin chen dang //
NK081(zhu)001:247: pad+ma rgya gram la sogs bzhi //
NK081(zhu)001:248: gzhal yas gdan dang bcas pa bskyed //
NK081(zhu)001:249: nyungs dkar blugs shing sngags brjod pas //
NK081(zhu)001:250: dbus su mi bskyod shar lho la //
NK081(zhu)001:251: kun bzang yab yum steng 'og gi //
NK081(zhu)001:252: thub pa nub dang byang du'o //
NK081(zhu)001:253: shar du rnam snang yab yum la //
NK081(zhu)001:254: sa snying byams pa yab yum lho //
NK081(zhu)001:255: gshin rje yab yum mi thub byang //
NK081(zhu)001:256: lhor ni 'byung ldan yab yum la //
NK081(zhu)001:257: nam snying sgrib sel yab yum gnyis //
NK081(zhu)001:258: shar dang lho bskyed stobs chen nub //
NK081(zhu)001:259: byol song thub pa byang du'o //
NK081(zhu)001:260: nub tu mtha' yas spyan ras dang //
NK081(zhu)001:261: kun bzang yab yum shar dang lho //
NK081(zhu)001:262: rta mgrin nub la yi dwags byang //
NK081(zhu)001:263: byang du don grub phyag rdo rje //
NK081(zhu)001:264: 'jam dpal yab yum shar lho dang //
NK081(zhu)001:265: nub tu bdud 'khyil lha min byang //
NK081(zhu)001:266: dbus kyi sngags bzlas snying po lnga //
NK081(zhu)001:267: phyi nang drang zhing nub tu blugs //
NK081(zhu)001:268: rnam snang spos la spong ba sku //
NK081(zhu)001:270: 'bru lnga mtha' yas gsung lnga dbang //
NK081(zhu)001:271: don grub sman lnga phrin las stobs //
NK081(zhu)001:272: chu blugs thim zhing byin gyis brlab //
NK081(zhu)001:273: kha rgyan t+r+aam gis byin brlabs te //
NK081(zhu)001:274: sgo sngags byang chub yan lag bdun //
NK081(zhu)001:275: mgul chings h'u bkod sems dpa' yi //
NK081(zhu)001:276: sngags bzlas dran pa'i gzungs su gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:277: gzugs thag ldan ye shes lnga //
NK081(zhu)001:278: 'phags pa'i lam dang yan lag brgyad //
NK081(zhu)001:279: thum pa'i sngags bzlas gzungs dang ldan //
NK081(zhu)001:280: phyag bzhes spyi btegs sngags bzlas pas //
NK081(zhu)001:281: mthu byin rab tu bskyed pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:282: mdun bzhag gzhal yas lha gsal gdab //
NK081(zhu)001:283: byin brlabs dbang bskur spyan drangs bstims //
NK081(zhu)001:284: phyag dang mchod pa la sogs bya //
NK081(zhu)001:285: smon lam gdab cing sbyor bzlas bskul //
NK081(zhu)001:286: rgyal mtshan rol mos sna drangs la //
NK081(zhu)001:287: bskor zhing bstod byas dbus su bzhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:288: des ni dgongs pa rdzogs pa yin //
NK081(zhu)001:289: slob dpon chen po dur khrod bde ba'i bum lung nas bskol nas /
NK081(zhu)001:291: zhung drung gis bsgyur ba'o ////tshe 'das rnam shes 'gugs pa'i lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:293: a yu ga ta bi dz+ny+aa na a tri kra /
NK081(zhu)001:294: a ti ka rak+sha da ka n+aa ma /
NK081(zhu)001:296: tshe 'das kyi rnam par shes pa 'gugs pa'i lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:297: ye shes thugs rjes 'dren pa chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:298: rgyud chen gnyis las gzhan don du //
NK081(zhu)001:299: gnas kyi cho ga gsungs pa yi //
NK081(zhu)001:300: zhi bas sgrol dang drag pos bskrad //
NK081(zhu)001:301: dngos gzhi dgug dang gsum du bstan //
NK081(zhu)001:302: myang 'das mchod la tshogs bsag cing //
NK081(zhu)001:303: chos skyong mchod la phrin las zhu //
NK081(zhu)001:304: rigs drug rnams la mchod sbyin bya //
NK081(zhu)001:305: bgegs rigs rnams la glud gtor btang //
NK081(zhu)001:307: phyi nang spang skong thams cad bsgrags //
NK081(zhu)001:308: khyad par gser skyems glud gtor gyis //
NK081(zhu)001:309: gshed ma'i rgyab rten ma byed bya //
NK081(zhu)001:310: za 'dre'i glud du btang la bslu //
NK081(zhu)001:311: shes pa rang thong cig ces bsgo //
NK081(zhu)001:312: yul lha rnams la stong gyis bya //
NK081(zhu)001:313: chu gtor glud gtor bden pa bsgrags //
NK081(zhu)001:314: gnyis pa bskrad pa gang yin pa //
NK081(zhu)001:315: bka' mi nyan cing bgegs byed pa'i //
NK081(zhu)001:316: lhan skyes 'dre dang yi dwags khog bsrung dang //
NK081(zhu)001:317: gshin rje khram 'dzin chos rgyal rtsis la sogs //
NK081(zhu)001:318: gson bdud gshin lcags byed pa thams cad la //
NK081(zhu)001:319: gnyen po lha dang 'dul byed btang ba dang //
NK081(zhu)001:320: sprul pa khro chu 'gugs pa'i mtshon cha dang //
NK081(zhu)001:321: rtog 'joms khro bo drag po'i las dang ni //
NK081(zhu)001:322: sgrol byed khro bo gtub pa'i mtshon cha dang //
NK081(zhu)001:323: brdung ba mtshon drug btab pa la sogs kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:324: bdud gcod srog len byed pa thams cad 'dul //
NK081(zhu)001:325: rno la gul gul yungs kar drag po'i sngags //
NK081(zhu)001:326: gsum pa dngos gzhi thabs dang rten yin te //
NK081(zhu)001:327: dri ma yid 'thad shes chags go log la //
NK081(zhu)001:328: pho mo'i rtags dang bcas pa'i tsog pu bya //
NK081(zhu)001:329: mtshan byang ming rus n+ri dang bcas pa bri //
NK081(zhu)001:330: zhi khro gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la //
NK081(zhu)001:331: phyag 'tshal skyabs gsol mthus btang dang //
NK081(zhu)001:332: byin rlabs gnas spar sgrib sbyong dang //
NK081(zhu)001:333: dbang bskur pa rnams sgrol gsol 'debs //
NK081(zhu)001:334: skyob pa'i gdugs dang lus tshad 'phan //
NK081(zhu)001:335: pad gdan smyug ma me long la //
NK081(zhu)001:336: bgegs kyis mi tshugs spos chen dang //
NK081(zhu)001:337: dri zhim bla tshags spos kyis bdug /rnam shes mi 'khyams rten du bya //
NK081(zhu)001:338: thabs la rnam pa bzhi yin te //
NK081(zhu)001:339: thugs rje stobs kyis dgug pa ni //
NK081(zhu)001:340: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:341: rang rgyud dag pa'i bden pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:342: rigs drug bar do gshegs la sogs //
NK081(zhu)001:343: gar skyes gang na gnas gyur kyang //
NK081(zhu)001:344: ngan song sgo gcod mtho ris kyi //
NK081(zhu)001:345: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gnyan drung du /
NK081(zhu)001:346: skad cig yud kyis dgug par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:347: sngags dang phyag rgyas dgug pa ni //
NK081(zhu)001:348: 'gug byed lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas //
NK081(zhu)001:349: a su n+ri tri pre du dang //
NK081(zhu)001:350: n+ri yam badz+ra am ku sha dzah bdun nam nyi shu rtsa gcig brjod //
NK081(zhu)001:351: shog skya rlung gis bskyod pa bzhin //
NK081(zhu)001:352: de nyid la yang khug par 'gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:353: rig pa rtsal gyis dgug pa ni //
NK081(zhu)001:354: bdag gi thugs ka'i dzah'aphrosa te //
NK081(zhu)001:355: de las sprul pa grangs med spros //
NK081(zhu)001:357: gshin gyi thang kha nas bzung ste //
NK081(zhu)001:358: bdag gi mdun du 'ongs par bsam //
NK081(zhu)001:360: tshad la phebs rtags gzhan du shes //
NK081(zhu)001:361: de nas rten la bstims byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:362: khog pa dbral zhing gnyis med bstim //
NK081(zhu)001:363: lcags kyus bzung nas zhags pas bcings //
NK081(zhu)001:364: lcags sgrog gis bsdoms dril dgyes bskyed //
NK081(zhu)001:365: skyo bas bar do'i 'du shes bsgyur //
NK081(zhu)001:366: sngon du srid pa'i sha gzugs can //
NK081(zhu)001:367: bar do'i shes pa bsgyur sla bas //
NK081(zhu)001:368: de nyid du ni shes par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:369: cho ga 'di dag mi ldan na //
NK081(zhu)001:371: sems can ma lus thams cad kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:372: bla med rang gnas thob par shog /rgya gar gyi
NK081(zhu)001:373: slob dpon bi ma la mi tri'i zhal snga nas
NK081(zhu)001:374: gsungs shing zhang drung dz+ny+aa ku m+aa ras bsgyur ba'o
NK081(zhu)001:375: ////rnam shes 'gugs pa'i gtan tshigs lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:377: a yu ga ta bi dz+ny+aa na he tu a
NK081(zhu)001:378: bri ta a ti ka rak+sha da ka na ma
NK081(zhu)001:380: tshe 'das kyi rnam par shes pa dgug pa'i gtan tshigs kyi lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:381: yi dam gyi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:382: gshin po'i don du las bya ba //
NK081(zhu)001:383: bsod nams rgyal po ma skyes dgras //
NK081(zhu)001:384: sum cu rtsa gsum lha gnas nas //
NK081(zhu)001:385: lha bu nor bu dri ma med //
NK081(zhu)001:386: sngon gyi pha bsad las snyegs kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:387: ngan song gnas su ltung ba las //
NK081(zhu)001:388: rten bcas shes pa bkug pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:389: ngan song gnas nas 'drongs pa bzhin //
NK081(zhu)001:390: de bas gang yin rten bcas nas //
NK081(zhu)001:391: ting 'dzin yid kyis bkug nas kyang //
NK081(zhu)001:392: rten sbyangs shes pa 'bras thob ces //
NK081(zhu)001:393: ston pa'i bka' las gsungs pa yin //
NK081(zhu)001:394: shes dgug thabs chen gzhan nas 'byung //
NK081(zhu)001:395: rtags la rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK081(zhu)001:396: rab la dngos dang 'bring la nyams //
NK081(zhu)001:397: tha ma rmi lam pra sgrub bya //
NK081(zhu)001:398: dang po stobs nus che ldan la //
NK081(zhu)001:399: bag chags lus de dag par snang //
NK081(zhu)001:400: dri ma ldog dang smyug ma 'gul //
NK081(zhu)001:401: me long mtshan byang 'dar ba srid //
NK081(zhu)001:402: nyams la nyams snang gong dang 'dra //
NK081(zhu)001:403: cha mthun snang nyams yid yul du //
NK081(zhu)001:404: rten de mi snyams yid yul du //
NK081(zhu)001:406: byang chub sems dang rab ldan pa'i //
NK081(zhu)001:407: skyes bu gzhan don cho ga mkhas //
NK081(zhu)001:408: gnas khang rten mchod yig 'bru lha //
NK081(zhu)001:409: bud+d+ha tsu ru tsu ru ma h+aa tsu ru ke s+w+aa h+aa /
NK081(zhu)001:410: 'bum tsho bcu gsum smra bcad bzlas //
NK081(zhu)001:411: dngos gzhi yar ngo'i dus bzang la //
NK081(zhu)001:412: sku khrus gsol zhing gsol ba gdab //
NK081(zhu)001:413: dkar gsum bza' zhing na bza' gsol //
NK081(zhu)001:414: byang chub chen por kha bltas la //
NK081(zhu)001:415: byang du nyal la rmi lam brtag /gar skye blta zhing gzhan don bya //
NK081(zhu)001:416: 'bum phrag bdun du bya ba rnams //
NK081(zhu)001:417: gzhung dang mthun par mkhas pas bya //
NK081(zhu)001:418: yang na mkha' 'gro'i pra phab ste //
NK081(zhu)001:419: gtsang zhing dri med gnas dag tu //
NK081(zhu)001:420: rten bshams mchod dang tshogs 'khor bskor //
NK081(zhu)001:421: me long dag bkru dri thig bya //
NK081(zhu)001:422: da ki lnga yi rang bzhin bsam //
NK081(zhu)001:423: da ma ru dang me long 'dzin //
NK081(zhu)001:424: mtho bong rgya skyegs thig le bya //
NK081(zhu)001:425: mig la ltas ston byug pas gsal //
NK081(zhu)001:426: rang gis khri tsho gsum du bzlas //
NK081(zhu)001:428: d+hu ru d+hu ru shag shag /tshal pa tshal pa /
NK081(zhu)001:430: ya shug ri nir ti phob phob ya ya /
NK081(zhu)001:431: de nas bu mo gtsang ma lnga //
NK081(zhu)001:432: khrus byas d+aa ki lnga ru bsam //
NK081(zhu)001:433: nyungs dkar sngags bcas drag tu dbab //
NK081(zhu)001:434: legs nyes ltas ston smra bar 'gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:435: dom dred stag byung rgyal po bskrad //
NK081(zhu)001:436: mkhas pas myur du 'dri zhing brtag /shin tu mngon shes gsal bar 'byung //
NK081(zhu)001:437: rtags mtshan ngan na bzlog par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:438: dge byas rang snang mngon thob 'gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:439: mi snang rkyen gsal bla med shog /rnam par shes pa khugs rtags dang //
NK081(zhu)001:440: rang gar skye ba brtag pa'i lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:441: gnod sbyin mo byang chub kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so ////gshin bla 'gugs pa man ngag lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:443: ya ma bi dz+ny+aa na ka rak+sha u pan te sha da ka na ma /
NK081(zhu)001:445: gshin bla 'gugs pa'i lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:446: zhi khro rab 'byams kyi lha tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:447: dus tha ma la rnal 'byor pa dgongs pa mi dran par /
NK081(zhu)001:448: kheng dregs dang yin lo 'gran pa'i dus so //
NK081(zhu)001:449: de'i dus gshin po'i bla dbab pa ni /
NK081(zhu)001:451: rdzas su phur pa khong gseng can gcig la //
NK081(zhu)001:452: dar sna lnga tshang bar btags la //
NK081(zhu)001:453: phur pa gshin po'i sems yin par bsgom /
NK081(zhu)001:454: dar sna lnga yid yin par bsgom //
NK081(zhu)001:455: khong gseng du bla 'khor bar bsgom //
NK081(zhu)001:456: sngags pa'i lus ri rab tsam du bsgom //
NK081(zhu)001:457: phur pa'i rtse mo gnam du bstan la //
NK081(zhu)001:458: steng tshangs pa'i gnas nas bla khugs par bsam //
NK081(zhu)001:459: phyogs mtshams thams cad du de ltar bsam /
NK081(zhu)001:460: phur pa rked pa la bskor la gshed ma'i lag nas bla phral bar bsgom /
NK081(zhu)001:461: bla gshed dang bral ba'i sngags ni /
NK081(zhu)001:466: zhab ni zhub ni thul can /
NK081(zhu)001:468: zho phud zhig 'og tu gzhug chang phud 'khur bas
NK081(zhu)001:469: kha bcad la bzhag /khye'u gtsang ma'am nye du la
NK081(zhu)001:470: sogs pa bdun khrus byas la /
NK081(zhu)001:472: mig btsum la bzhag /spre'u'i 'jug ma dang rna ba //
NK081(zhu)001:473: phag blo skyeg gi rnga ma //
NK081(zhu)001:474: bdag sngags pa'i lus la bcangs //
NK081(zhu)001:479: pro mor dun shag ta dul byil nan //
NK081(zhu)001:482: ma ban ya ne shag /ces brjod cing /
NK081(zhu)001:484: shag po'i thod ras gtor bas //
NK081(zhu)001:488: bu lon smra ngo bo dang gson la 'dug gi smra /
NK081(zhu)001:489: thams cad kyis der mi dri //
NK081(zhu)001:490: bla ma'i nye drung snying reg mas dri thams cad du mi bya /
NK081(zhu)001:491: dge sbyor bung che ba'am dam tshig 'brel pa bya'o //
NK081(zhu)001:493: blon po 'gos rgan don du mdzad pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:494: gshin bla 'gugs pa'i lung phran zhes bya ba rdzogs so ////thugs rje chen po sbyang ba'i lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:496: ma h+aa ka ru a h+aa a ka rak+sha da ka n+aa ma /
NK081(zhu)001:498: thugs rje chen pos sbyang ba'i lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:499: bcom ldan 'das sbyong byed thugs rje'i rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:500: ye shes rang gnas 'dus ma byas //
NK081(zhu)001:501: cir yang snang bas gzhan du 'gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:502: gnyis la drug snang bzhi nyid du //
NK081(zhu)001:503: bar ma srid pa'i mtshams sbyor zhing //
NK081(zhu)001:504: 'khor bar srid pa'i rgyu rnams ni //
NK081(zhu)001:505: rin chen tsit+ta'i pho brang nang //
NK081(zhu)001:506: rtsa ba sa bon dbyibs dang 'od //
NK081(zhu)001:507: so sor srid pa'i nyon mongs drug /rang dang gzhan gyis bsags shing gnas //
NK081(zhu)001:508: thugs rje chen po'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK081(zhu)001:509: zab mo'i lung gis sbyangs byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:510: sngon du bum par bsnyen byas na //
NK081(zhu)001:511: skad cig drag po'i lha gsal nas //
NK081(zhu)001:512: rnam shes bsdu zhing bar chad bsal //
NK081(zhu)001:513: phyi nang sngags kyi sbyor ba yis //
NK081(zhu)001:514: rgyud drug 'dus pa'i dug sbyangs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:515: ting 'dzin skabs bsgyur lung tshig bskul //
NK081(zhu)001:516: mthar phyin pa nas gzhan don dbang //
NK081(zhu)001:517: las kyi mjug sdud rdzogs par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:518: bi ma la'i bdun tshigs gnas bu chung //
NK081(zhu)001:520: a tsa ra dz+ny+aa nas zhus te bsgyur cing gtan la phab pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:521: bi ma la yis 'brel ba phyi ma'i don du bdun tshigs rtsa ba mdzad /
NK081(zhu)001:522: +thii ////thabs dang shes rab mda' gzhu'i lung phra na /
NK081(zhu)001:523: ye shes rang snang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:525: steng gi lha bran thams cad 'chi //
NK081(zhu)001:526: de yang phyi nang gsang ba ste //
NK081(zhu)001:527: phyi ni dngos su snang ba lab //
NK081(zhu)001:528: rgyud dang byin rlabs yon tan gsum //
NK081(zhu)001:529: rgyu ni 'od ma las byas pa //
NK081(zhu)001:530: mchog ma rten cing 'brel bar byas //
NK081(zhu)001:531: byin rlabs yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK081(zhu)001:533: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod brtson 'grus //
NK081(zhu)001:534: bsam gtan dang ni shes rab thabs //
NK081(zhu)001:535: smon lam stobs dang ye shes so //
NK081(zhu)001:536: dbus su shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK081(zhu)001:537: gzhan ni go rim bzhin du'o //
NK081(zhu)001:538: kun kyang kha dog ser mo ste //
NK081(zhu)001:539: g.yas pa chos 'chad phyag rgya la //
NK081(zhu)001:540: g.yon pa po ti bsnams pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:541: g.yas pa sa nu he ru ka /g.yas gsum rdo
NK081(zhu)001:542: rje rnge'u chung mda' //g.yon gsum dril bu ral gri
NK081(zhu)001:543: gzhu // g.yon du yum chen nam mkha' spyan //
NK081(zhu)001:545: dam rgyan mchog ma g.yas pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:546: khro chen rat+na he ru ka /ser nag zhal gsum phyag drug pa //
NK081(zhu)001:547: rin chen tri shul dang po gnyis //
NK081(zhu)001:548: bar gnyis rdo rje dung dmar 'khrug /tha ma gnyis na ti ra rnga //
NK081(zhu)001:549: mchog ma g.yon na rtsi ri te //
NK081(zhu)001:550: ser mo lag na mda' gazhu'o //
NK081(zhu)001:551: rgyud g.yas pad+ma he ru ka /g.yon na rdo rje sgra sgrogs la //
NK081(zhu)001:552: gnyis ka dbu stong phyag stong ste //
NK081(zhu)001:553: phyag na po ti bsnams pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:554: g.yas pa mtheb kyi 'byed tshul la //
NK081(zhu)001:555: zhal nas chos kyi sgra sgrogs pas //
NK081(zhu)001:556: theg pa sna tshogs ston pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:557: mda' yang don gsum gong dang 'dra //
NK081(zhu)001:558: ltong nas made'u'i bar du ni //
NK081(zhu)001:559: h'u mdzad la sogs khro bcu bsam //
NK081(zhu)001:560: bdag po bzhi dang don mdzad bzhi //
NK081(zhu)001:561: thabs dang shes rab khro bo gnyis //
NK081(zhu)001:562: pha rol phyin pa bcu po dang //
NK081(zhu)001:563: yab yum tshul du sbyor ba ste //
NK081(zhu)001:564: ltong rgyud sbyor bar byas pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:565: yab yum kun kyang sbyor ba mdzad //
NK081(zhu)001:566: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK081(zhu)001:567: smyug ma'i sbubs na yar la drangs //
NK081(zhu)001:568: shes pa made'u'i rtse la blangs //
NK081(zhu)001:569: des kyang spor ba'i las rnams byed //
NK081(zhu)001:570: mi dge bcu po tshar bcad nas //
NK081(zhu)001:571: dge ba bcu la bkod nas ni //
NK081(zhu)001:572: dbang bcu mthar phyin sa bcu rdzogs //
NK081(zhu)001:573: gdengs dang mi ldan thun mong ste //
NK081(zhu)001:574: srin po lag nas mtshon thogs 'dra //
NK081(zhu)001:575: bi ma la mi tras pa h'u mdzad rtog pa
NK081(zhu)001:576: phyi ma las btus nas mdzad pa rdzogs so ////gnas
NK081(zhu)001:577: kyi sa dang lam gyi lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:579: b+hu ma ma ra ga ba da a ti ka rak+sha da ka n+aa ma /
NK081(zhu)001:581: gnas kyi sa dang lam gyi lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:582: ye shes rang gnas kyi rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:583: tshe 'das gnas bstod cho ga las //
NK081(zhu)001:584: spyir du lung las byung ba yi //
NK081(zhu)001:585: thugs rje gtor sbyin dkyil 'khor dang //
NK081(zhu)001:588: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK081(zhu)001:589: rgyud drug sgrol ba'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK081(zhu)001:590: gu ya dbang gi da la drug /re re'ang lnga lngar shes byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:591: sgrib lam sa dbang gnas bzhir bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:592: las sgrib dag cing tshogs lam zhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:593: dang po'i sa non rten dbang thob //
NK081(zhu)001:594: sgrib sbyang tshogs kyi gnas bzhir bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:595: skye gnas sgrib dag sbyor lam zhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:596: mos spyod sa non rtog 'joms dbang //
NK081(zhu)001:597: stong pa chos nyid gnas bzhir bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:598: dang po las dag mthong lam zhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:599: rab dag'i sa non lha dbang thob //
NK081(zhu)001:600: rtog 'joms khro bo'i gnas bzhir bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:601: shes bya'i sgrib dag sgoms lam zhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:602: mi rtogs sa non gsang dbang thob //
NK081(zhu)001:603: byin rlabs thugs rje'i gnas bzhir bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:604: shes sgrib 'bring dag thar lam zhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:605: sa bcu nyid non shes dbang thob //
NK081(zhu)001:606: bsgral ba rigs me gnas bzhir bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:607: shes bya'i sgrib dag phyir lam zhugs //
NK081(zhu)001:608: sangs rgyas sa non bde ba thob //
NK081(zhu)001:609: rang gnas gdal ba'i gnas bzhir bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:610: khyad par rgyud drug sgrol ba ni //
NK081(zhu)001:611: lung gi tshad mas sbyangs pa las //
NK081(zhu)001:612: lha mi'i theg pa tshogs gnas bzhi //
NK081(zhu)001:613: sbyin pa'i dal 'brel skye sgrib dag /dgra bcom sa non gzhan thob min //
NK081(zhu)001:614: nang pa phar dgongs rnam pa lnga //
NK081(zhu)001:615: kun tu 'od kyi sa bsgral bas //
NK081(zhu)001:616: tshogs lam byang sems theg pa ste //
NK081(zhu)001:617: chos nyid gnas bstod bar mtshams 'brel //
NK081(zhu)001:618: yongs rdzogs dbang thob nyon rang dag /kun sa chos sku stong ye shes //
NK081(zhu)001:619: stug po bkod par bsgral skabs su //
NK081(zhu)001:620: sbyor lam phyi rgyud ring nges bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:621: sgrol byed chus dbang nyon sgrib dag /stug po longs sku me long gsal //
NK081(zhu)001:622: pad+ma can du bsgral skabs su //
NK081(zhu)001:623: mthong lam ma yog khro nas bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:624: rgyur 'grel gsang bdag kun 'gro dag /pad+ma mngon byang mnyam pa nyid //
NK081(zhu)001:625: 'khor lo tshogs chen bsgral skabs su //
NK081(zhu)001:626: sgom lam a nu phyin thugs rje //
NK081(zhu)001:627: rdo rje dbyings sher lhan skyes dag /
NK081(zhu)001:628: 'khor lo sprul sku bya grub gsal //
NK081(zhu)001:629: ye shes bla mar bsgral skabs su //
NK081(zhu)001:630: mthar lam a tir rang gnas bstod //
NK081(zhu)001:631: lhun grub bde chen rang gnas dag /kun bzang rdo rje kun rtog gsal //
NK081(zhu)001:632: mdor na lam thog gnas bzhi dal //
NK081(zhu)001:633: dbang sgrib sa non sku dang ni //
NK081(zhu)001:634: ye shes dang ni dgu zhes bya //
NK081(zhu)001:635: gdul bya rang mtshan mngon thob shog /rgya gar gyi
NK081(zhu)001:636: mkhan po bi ma la mi tra'i dgongs pa las
NK081(zhu)001:637: / dri med zla shar nyid kyis gags sel bco
NK081(zhu)001:638: brgyad pa'i rjes thogs su gsung pa rdzogs so ////h'u
NK081(zhu)001:639: nyid ring por spar ba'i lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:640: 'khor dang mya ngan 'das pa'i bcud 'dus shing //
NK081(zhu)001:641: bag chags tshogs 'joms yon tan rdzogs par ldan //
NK081(zhu)001:642: brjod med h'u la gus pas phyag 'tshal nas //
NK081(zhu)001:643: rang gnas ma mthong log 'khyams don phyir du //
NK081(zhu)001:644: yi ge h'u gi mtshan nyid bstan par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:645: khong nas gab pa'i don 'byin bya ba'i phyir //
NK081(zhu)001:646: h'u nyid rnam gsum tshul du shes byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:647: gnas dang mngon byed mthar phyin gyis //
NK081(zhu)001:649: gnas pa dbyings sgra don nyid do //
NK081(zhu)001:651: dbyug pa ha gnyis dbang sdud ring po dag /rin chen smug po'i nang nas srog shing tshul //
NK081(zhu)001:652: 'byi ma yab kyi byang chub sems //
NK081(zhu)001:653: 'du ma yum gyi byang chub sems //
NK081(zhu)001:654: nga tshes gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK081(zhu)001:655: dbyug pa gnyis ni rtog pa'i mchog /ha yis don byed rin chen gsal bar byed //
NK081(zhu)001:656: hu yis thams cad sdud par byed //
NK081(zhu)001:657: zhabs kyu yis ni gnyis med 'gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:658: ring po de nyid kun mkhas pa //
NK081(zhu)001:659: thog ma dbu ma rnam gnyis te //
NK081(zhu)001:660: sgra dang sgra tshul rnam gnyis po //
NK081(zhu)001:661: gang dang gang du brjod pa'i sgra //
NK081(zhu)001:662: ring por 'khyams pas ring po nyid //
NK081(zhu)001:663: sgra rnams mtha' stong ji bzhin du //
NK081(zhu)001:664: thig le rtsol bar bcas pa dag /gdod nas snying po byang chub bo //
NK081(zhu)001:665: kun gzhi las 'das snying po mchog /ye shes chen
NK081(zhu)001:666: po bde ba'i mchog /don gyi sems nyid 'dus ma
NK081(zhu)001:667: byas // yi ge yid 'ong du snang ba'o //
NK081(zhu)001:668: dbu ma rnam gnyis shes byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:669: bdag gzhan don du nyams su blangs //
NK081(zhu)001:670: bdag gi nyams su blangs pa'i don //
NK081(zhu)001:671: phyi nang gsang ba gsum du gsungs //
NK081(zhu)001:672: rang lus yi ge h'u du bsdu //
NK081(zhu)001:673: h'u nyid a yis mtshams sbyar nas //
NK081(zhu)001:674: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyur gyur te //
NK081(zhu)001:675: dmigs su med pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK081(zhu)001:676: rin chen smug po'i gzhal g.yas su //
NK081(zhu)001:677: a ba d+hu ti'i rtsa gnas su //
NK081(zhu)001:678: rnam gnyis chos kun h'u du bsdu //
NK081(zhu)001:679: bdud bzhi'i sras su bskyed nas kyang //
NK081(zhu)001:680: bde ba chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK081(zhu)001:681: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK081(zhu)001:682: bdag bde ba yi klong yongs su //
NK081(zhu)001:683: h'u nyid zla ba'i ngo 'byor tshe //
NK081(zhu)001:684: rtsol ba rngub sdom sbyor ba yis //
NK081(zhu)001:686: rnam shes 'pho bar gyur pa'i tshe //
NK081(zhu)001:687: rnam shes gsum po h'u du bsdu //
NK081(zhu)001:688: h'u nyid na bza' lam byung nas //
NK081(zhu)001:689: bde gshegs thugs kar thim nas kyang //
NK081(zhu)001:690: rnam shes ba gar shul byung ste //
NK081(zhu)001:691: rgyal ba'i sras su rang nyid bskyed //
NK081(zhu)001:692: bde ba chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK081(zhu)001:693: sangs rgyas sa la gdon mi za //
NK081(zhu)001:694: dngos po gzhan gyi don du ni //
NK081(zhu)001:695: 'khor rgyud rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK081(zhu)001:696: rnam par shes pa bsdus pa yi //
NK081(zhu)001:697: rnam shes h'u gi rtag pa ste //
NK081(zhu)001:698: skur gyur ye shes sems dpa' la //
NK081(zhu)001:700: rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa //
NK081(zhu)001:701: leb rgan h'u gis mtshams sbyar nas //
NK081(zhu)001:702: sras su gyur pa bde ba'i mchog /h'u 'dod mkhar nub grub par 'gyur //
NK081(zhu)001:703: tha ma 'bras bu mthar thug don //
NK081(zhu)001:704: ye shes dgu yi bdag nyid la //
NK081(zhu)001:705: yi ge h'u dang mtshon par snang //
NK081(zhu)001:706: kun gsal rang bzhin med dang dngos po bral //
NK081(zhu)001:707: 'khor ba'i skyon rnams ma spangs dbyings su dag /thams
NK081(zhu)001:708: cad gsal dang ma rmongs yon tan lhun gyis rdzogs
NK081(zhu)001:709: // dngos po mthar mi gnas dang sdug bsngal ngang gis bral //
NK081(zhu)001:710: chos rnams ma lus ye nas dbyer med la //
NK081(zhu)001:711: 'dzin med rdo rje sngon po ye shes sku //
NK081(zhu)001:712: ma bsgrubs thos pa bsgrub bya dam pa'o //
NK081(zhu)001:713: bdag 'dra dman pas bsdu bar mi 'os kyang //
NK081(zhu)001:714: khungs dang man ngag rjes su legs 'brangs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:715: gsum shes gnyis blangs bsgrub par bya ba'i thabs //
NK081(zhu)001:716: tshig bsdus don rgyas blo mchog don bsdus pas //
NK081(zhu)001:717: phyi rabs sems can bde mchog mngon thob shog /phangs med ser sna spangs dang rtogs pa gsal //
NK081(zhu)001:718: gsang thub spyod pa dam dang dam tshig bsrung //
NK081(zhu)001:719: de 'dra'i rnal 'byor gcig dang 'phrad par shog /h'u
NK081(zhu)001:720: nyid ring por spar ba'i lung phran zhes bya ba
NK081(zhu)001:721: / rgya gar gyi mkhan po bi ma la mi
NK081(zhu)001:722: tras mdzad pa rdzogs so ////bcol dang bskang ba'i lung
NK081(zhu)001:723: / phran / bcom ldan sgrol byed thugs rje'i rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:724: gnas lung rgyud kyi gshegs gsol dang //
NK081(zhu)001:725: bcol dang bskang ba'i lung phran ni //
NK081(zhu)001:726: pri pa man tra pa tra bud+d+ha s+pha ra na ya ma /
NK081(zhu)001:727: zhes pa dri ma dang mtshan byang gi rdo rje
NK081(zhu)001:728: sems dpa' phye la chos kyi dbyings su gshegs su
NK081(zhu)001:729: gsol / de nas nyon mongs ba'i sems can 'khor
NK081(zhu)001:730: ba gnas pa rnams snying po byang chub la dgod
NK081(zhu)001:731: par thugs rjes bzung zhing las bcol ba ni /
NK081(zhu)001:733: kha dog sna lnga'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:734: gzugs brnyan da la dngos su bris pa'i mthus //
NK081(zhu)001:735: rang bzhin da la chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:736: ting 'dzin da la lhun gyis grub par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:737: snod kyi 'jig rten dngos po cir snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:738: dbang chen gzhal yas khang du bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK081(zhu)001:739: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:740: 'og min gnas su lhun gyis grub par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:741: phung po lnga dang 'byung lnga cir snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:742: rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:743: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:744: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:745: rnam shes dbang po'i yul du cir snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:746: sems dpa' yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:747: thams cad lha dang lha mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:748: rgyal ba'i sras su lhun gyis grub par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:749: phyin ci log rtog dngos po cir snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:750: sgo ba yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:751: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:752: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:753: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po ci snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:754: thub pa drug tu bsgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:755: longs spyod rdzogs dang sprul sku'i don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:756: sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:757: yul dang sems kyi rnam pa cir snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:758: kun bzang yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK081(zhu)001:759: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:760: chos sku 'gyur med lhun gyis grub par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:761: lha dang bdag dang gzhan du cir snang yang //
NK081(zhu)001:762: bde gshegs spyan drangs phyag 'tshal mchod pa'i mthus //
NK081(zhu)001:763: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK081(zhu)001:764: rig 'dzin rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par bcol //
NK081(zhu)001:766: byang sems bde ba chen po'i da la nas //
NK081(zhu)001:767: bcom ldan kun tu bzang po la //
NK081(zhu)001:768: tshe 'das yid kyis thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:769: bde ba chen po'i dngos grub rtsol //
NK081(zhu)001:770: mkha' mnyam klong gi da la nas //
NK081(zhu)001:771: yum chen kun tu bzang mo la //
NK081(zhu)001:772: tshe 'das chos kyi thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:773: gnyis su med pa'i dngos grub rtsol //
NK081(zhu)001:774: spros med thig le yangs pa chen po nas //
NK081(zhu)001:775: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK081(zhu)001:776: gzugs kyi phung pos thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:777: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes la //
NK081(zhu)001:778: de bzhin rigs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:779: bcom ldan rdo rje mi bskyod la //
NK081(zhu)001:780: rnam shes phung pos thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:781: me long lta bu'i ye shes la //
NK081(zhu)001:782: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub rtsol //
NK081(zhu)001:783: bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan la //
NK081(zhu)001:784: tshor ba'i phung pos thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:785: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes las //
NK081(zhu)001:786: rin chen rigs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:787: bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas la //
NK081(zhu)001:788: 'du shes phung pos thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:789: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes la //
NK081(zhu)001:790: pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:791: bcom ldan don yod grub pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:792: 'du byed phung pos thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:793: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes las //
NK081(zhu)001:794: las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:795: kun tu bzang mo la sogs yum lnga la //
NK081(zhu)001:796: 'byung ba lnga yis thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:797: skye ba med pa'i dbyings nyid las //
NK081(zhu)001:798: rigs kyi yum lnga'i dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:799: chos nyid rigs pas rtogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK081(zhu)001:800: sa snying la sogs sems dpa' brgyad rnams la //
NK081(zhu)001:801: rnam shes yul dang bcas pas thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:802: ye shes brgyad kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:803: tshad med bzhi yi da la nas //
NK081(zhu)001:804: 'joms pa chen po bzhi rnams kyang //
NK081(zhu)001:805: tshad med lha mo bzhi rnams la //
NK081(zhu)001:806: phyin ci log bzhis thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:807: 'phrin las bzhi yi dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:808: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu nas //
NK081(zhu)001:809: 'gro ba drug gi sgrib sbyang ba'i //
NK081(zhu)001:810: bcom ldan thub pa drug rnams la //
NK081(zhu)001:811: nyon mongs drug gis thugs dam bskang //
NK081(zhu)001:812: ye shes drug gi dngos grub stsol //
NK081(zhu)001:813: bcol dang bskang ba'i lung phran /
NK081(zhu)001:814: h'u mdzad phyi ma'i lung nyi tshe zhig rdzogs so
NK081(zhu)001:815: ////dge ba'i bshes gnyen la mnga' dbul gi lung phran
NK081(zhu)001:816: / rgyal ba zhi khro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:817: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la mnga' dbul ba'i lung phran ni /
NK081(zhu)001:818: spyi'i gzhung dang mthun par byas la /
NK081(zhu)001:819: dbang rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i rjes la /
NK081(zhu)001:820: rig 'dzin gyi gral du mnga' dbul ba /
NK081(zhu)001:821: zhi ba'i tshogs kyi bar du /
NK081(zhu)001:823: bro gar rtse 'jo'i tshig lcogs na legs /
NK081(zhu)001:825: a thabs dang shes rab ces pas /
NK081(zhu)001:826: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mos //
NK081(zhu)001:827: rkang pa'i stabs byed lag gar bsgyur //
NK081(zhu)001:828: ces pa'i tshig gi zhabs su /
NK081(zhu)001:831: pu tsa'i lha mo bcu gnyis dang /
NK081(zhu)001:832: su ra to bcu drug gi gar bya /
NK081(zhu)001:833: bro gar 'du 'phro'i mchod pa dbul ba ni /
NK081(zhu)001:836: rig 'dzin rdo rje'i gral du gshegs pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:837: bro gar 'du 'phro'i phyag rgyas mnga' dbul bas //
NK081(zhu)001:838: 'dzum lam nam mkhar 'gro ba thob par shog /
NK081(zhu)001:839: s+pha ra na ma h+aa pu tsa h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:840: ta th+aa thams kyi thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK081(zhu)001:841: rig 'dzin rdo rje ch+gee khyod la bro gar 'du 'phro'i mnga' dbul bas /
NK081(zhu)001:842: rig 'dzin gral nas thogs pa med par bya bzhin mkha' la 'phur ba dang /
NK081(zhu)001:843: sa la byi bzhin 'dzul ba dang /
NK081(zhu)001:844: rdzu 'phrul gyis 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i skal ba
NK081(zhu)001:845: dang ldan par gyur cig /de nas glu tshig sgra
NK081(zhu)001:847: sgra bsgyur mnyam nyid mi g.yo zhes pa nas /
NK081(zhu)001:848: dam tshig mchog gi dngos grub stsol ces pa'i bar brjod do /
NK081(zhu)001:850: rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa phul bas mnyes te /
NK081(zhu)001:853: rig 'dzin rdo rje'i gral du gshegs pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:854: sgra tshig phyag rgyas mnga' dbul bas //
NK081(zhu)001:855: gsung lnga chos kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK081(zhu)001:856: pra na na ma h'u su ka h'u h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:858: rig 'dzin rdo rje'i gral du gshegs pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:859: glu tshig sgra yi mchod pas mnga' dbul bas //
NK081(zhu)001:860: snang mtha' gsung gi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK081(zhu)001:861: pra ma na ma h+aa su ka h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:862: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rje chen pos byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK081(zhu)001:863: rig 'dzin rdo rje ch+gee khyod la /
NK081(zhu)001:864: glu tshig gi sgra dang phyag rgyas mnga' dbul bas /
NK081(zhu)001:865: rig 'dzin rdo rje 'chang gi gral nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK081(zhu)001:866: 'gro ba tha dag gi shes pa'i rgyud khrol ba'i
NK081(zhu)001:867: skal pa dang ldan par gyur cig /de nas rgyan
NK081(zhu)001:868: dang bgo ba'i phyag rgyas mnga' dbul te /
NK081(zhu)001:871: rig 'dzin gral du gshegs pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:872: rgyan dang bgo ba'i mnga' dbul bas //
NK081(zhu)001:873: phas kyi rgol bas mi tshugs thob par shog /de
NK081(zhu)001:874: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rje chen pos
NK081(zhu)001:876: rig 'dzin rdo rje ch+gee khyod la /
NK081(zhu)001:877: rgyan dang bgo ba la sogs pa'i mnga' dbul bas /
NK081(zhu)001:878: phas kyi rgol bas mi tshugs pa'i skal ba dang
NK081(zhu)001:879: ldan par gyur cig /de nas bza' ba dang btung
NK081(zhu)001:881: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /ces pas 'dod yon dang /
NK081(zhu)001:882: dgyes mchog gi zhal zas bstab la mnga' dbul ba ni /
NK081(zhu)001:885: rig 'dzin gral du gshegs pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:886: bza' dang btung ba'i mnga' dbul bas //
NK081(zhu)001:887: phyag rgya chen po'i lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK081(zhu)001:888: las dang 'bras bu'i dngos grub thob par shog /de
NK081(zhu)001:889: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rje chen pos
NK081(zhu)001:891: rig 'dzin rdo rje ch+gee khyod la /
NK081(zhu)001:892: bza' dang btung ba'i mnga' dbul bas /
NK081(zhu)001:893: rig 'dzin rdo rje 'chang gyi gral du /
NK081(zhu)001:894: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku thob nas /
NK081(zhu)001:896: longs spyod cing 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i skal ba
NK081(zhu)001:897: dang ldan par gyur cig /de nas +aa li k+aa
NK081(zhu)001:898: li'i phyag rgyas mnga' dbul ba ni /
NK081(zhu)001:900: bo d+hi yod na legs so //
NK081(zhu)001:901: med na me long khud du bdud rtsi blugs la
NK081(zhu)001:902: bdag gtso bo yab yum gyis byang sems su bsams
NK081(zhu)001:903: la / dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med sbyar //
NK081(zhu)001:904: thabs dang shes rab 'khyil pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:907: ces bdud brtsi gtor zhing dbul ba ni /
NK081(zhu)001:910: rig 'dzin rdo rje'i gral du gshegs pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:911: +aa li k+aa li'i phyag rgyas mnga' dbul bas //
NK081(zhu)001:912: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin mdzad pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:913: lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub thob nas kyang //
NK081(zhu)001:914: las dang 'bras bu thams cad rdzogs par shog /de
NK081(zhu)001:915: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rje chen pos
NK081(zhu)001:917: rig 'dzin rdo rje ch+gee khyod la a li k+aa li'i phyag rgyas mnga' dbul bas /
NK081(zhu)001:918: rig 'dzin mdzad pa spyod lam mthar phyin par gyur
NK081(zhu)001:919: cig /rig 'dzin mnga' dbul ba'i lung phran zhes bya
NK081(zhu)001:920: ba rdzogs so ////tshe 'das rnam rtog gri 'dul lung
NK081(zhu)001:922: a yu ga ta bi kalasa&a&a&a ma ri g+ha ri a ti ka rak+sha da ka n+aa ma /
NK081(zhu)001:924: tshe 'das pa'i rnam par rtog gri 'dul ba'i lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:925: dpal grol byed rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:926: gnas ni sa bdag gi gling /
NK081(zhu)001:928: bgegs kyi 'dun sa ma yin par //
NK081(zhu)001:929: sa chog dang cha gsum gser skyems btang /
NK081(zhu)001:931: hom gyi thab rtsig pa dang /
NK081(zhu)001:932: bsreg rdzas gzhung bzhin du bsog /khyad par ra sog la gshed ma bgegs kyi ming rus bri /
NK081(zhu)001:933: shog bu gru gsum la gshed kyi ling+ga bri /
NK081(zhu)001:935: mtshon gam dung bzhag zhi khro'i phrin las gzhung bsrang /
NK081(zhu)001:936: tshogs zin nas pho nya'i skabs su gri thabs bcu gsum dang /
NK081(zhu)001:937: dgra bgegs dgug cing bsgral te /
NK081(zhu)001:939: mda' gi gzer ba me gri tshig 'bar dang //
NK081(zhu)001:940: rta gri zhun mar dal gri dub pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:941: chu gri 'dar shang gad gri 'phyam pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:942: pu gri 'gab dmar gri gri smug po dang //
NK081(zhu)001:943: thog gri tshig pa 'gags gri mig 'bur dang //
NK081(zhu)001:944: nibs gri subs pa rdo gri gdan dmar dang //
NK081(zhu)001:945: dug gri spos pa la sogs rkyen rnams dang //
NK081(zhu)001:946: phung pa'i sri dang za ba'i 'dre la sogs //
NK081(zhu)001:947: gzugs can dgra dang gzugs med bgegs rnams dang //
NK081(zhu)001:948: rgan rgon gri sri gzhon bdud ma lus pa //
NK081(zhu)001:949: gnod byed dmigs pa gnas nas khug la shog /ces
NK081(zhu)001:950: pa la sogs pa phur bskor dang gtor thun dang
NK081(zhu)001:951: / mtshon cha'i char bas btul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:952: bsreg rdzas byin gyis brlabs rnams ni //
NK081(zhu)001:953: me lha'i tshogs la rgyas par dbul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:954: me lha'i lto bar lha bskyed la /
NK081(zhu)001:955: dal gyi lha 'god cing gri 'dul ste /
NK081(zhu)001:958: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i rgyun gcod cing //
NK081(zhu)001:959: tshe 'das gri yi bag chags bsreg tu gsol //
NK081(zhu)001:960: dam nyams dam skong dbang dang dngos grub rnams //
NK081(zhu)001:961: tshe 'das 'di la 'grub par stsal du gsol //
NK081(zhu)001:963: rgyas par lha re'i bstod pa'i gzhug tu gri thabs bcu gsum gyi tshig kyang gzhug cing /
NK081(zhu)001:964: gshed kyi ling+ga dang ming byang bsreg go //
NK081(zhu)001:965: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sa bon a ni su tri pre du drug bris la bsreg cing /
NK081(zhu)001:967: zhe sdang rgyu byas mi dge bcu yi las //
NK081(zhu)001:968: dmyal ba tsha grang la sogs rang bsad dang //
NK081(zhu)001:969: dmyal ba'i las nyon bag chags gri 'dul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:970: tshe 'das 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thar gyur cig /h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:971: ser snas rgyu byas mi dge bcu yi las //
NK081(zhu)001:972: yi dwags bkres skom la sogs ngal dub dang //
NK081(zhu)001:973: yi dwags las nyon bag chags gri 'dul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:974: tshe 'das 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thar gyur cig /h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:975: gti mug rgyu byas mi dge bcu yi las //
NK081(zhu)001:976: dud 'gro glen lkugs la sogs bkol spyad dang //
NK081(zhu)001:977: dud 'gro'i las nyon bag chags gri 'dul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:978: tshe 'das 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thar gyur cig /h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:979: 'dod chags rgyu byas mi dge bcu yi las //
NK081(zhu)001:980: mi yi chags sdang la sogs rgyud nyams dang //
NK081(zhu)001:981: mi yi las nyon bag chags gri 'dul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:982: tshe 'das 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thar gyur cig /h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:983: nga rgyal rgyu byas mi dge bcu yi las //
NK081(zhu)001:984: lha min 'thab rtsod la sogs khro 'khrug dang //
NK081(zhu)001:985: lha min las nyon bag chags gri 'dul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:986: tshe 'das 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thar gyur cig /h'u /
NK081(zhu)001:987: phrag dog rgyu byas mi dge bcu yi las //
NK081(zhu)001:988: lha yi 'chi 'pho la sogs ltung 'jigs dang //
NK081(zhu)001:989: lha yi las nyon bag chags gri 'dul lo //
NK081(zhu)001:990: tshe 'das 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thar gyur cig /de nas sman gyis gso ba ni /
NK081(zhu)001:991: mtshan byang dang bar snang la gtor zhing /
NK081(zhu)001:993: tshe 'das gri yi skyon gyis phog pa yi //
NK081(zhu)001:994: rma rnams bdud rtsi sman gyi sos gyur cig /gnyan rigs lha klu sman btsan bdud sde brgyad //
NK081(zhu)001:995: mi mthun gri dang me lces rmas pa sman gyis gso //
NK081(zhu)001:996: a mri ta h'u de nas lung las byung ba'i spar chog kun rdzogs par bya'o //
NK081(zhu)001:1001: gang yang rung bar dong gru gsum brus la /
NK081(zhu)001:1002: gong gi ra sog la gshed ma'i ming rus bris pa de /
NK081(zhu)001:1003: sngags kyis bsdus la gzhug rdo rje rgya gram gyis khar bcad cing /
NK081(zhu)001:1005: mnan cing gzer ba'i dus la babs /
NK081(zhu)001:1006: nam yang thon par ma gyur cig /ces las bzhi'i bro brdung ngo //
NK081(zhu)001:1007: de nas gri bzlog mtshon bsgyur byas te /
NK081(zhu)001:1008: gtor ma dang me dang go mtshon mang pos dgra phyogs su bsdigs shing /
NK081(zhu)001:1010: bka' bsgyur gyi gsham du gong gi tshig rnams kyang brjod do //
NK081(zhu)001:1011: las 'dir gri thabs thams cad ma btul nas //
NK081(zhu)001:1012: mi rabs bdun du mi brgyud grir 'chi bas //
NK081(zhu)001:1013: de phyir btul ba'i yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK081(zhu)001:1014: rigs drug gnas su skyes kyang gri las thar //
NK081(zhu)001:1015: tshe 'phos lus barjesa bde ba'i gnas su 'gro //
NK081(zhu)001:1016: tshe 'das kyi rnam rtog gri 'dul ba'i lung phran
NK081(zhu)001:1017: zhes bya ba u rgyan pad+mas sems can gyi don
NK081(zhu)001:1018: du mdzad pa rdzogs so ////sbubs 'jug bshig pa sri
NK081(zhu)001:1019: 'dul lung phran / sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das zhi khro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:1021: sri can la gtor ma gtong na /
NK081(zhu)001:1022: sri can de gang nye ba'i kha phor kha chags tu 'bru sna lnga'am /
NK081(zhu)001:1023: 'gugs gzhug tshad la chang bu lnga'am /
NK081(zhu)001:1024: bdun nam nyer gcig bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:1035: de'i khar thal ba bag tsam blug la /
NK081(zhu)001:1036: de nas bdag nyid yi dam gyi nga rgyal dang ldan par byas la /
NK081(zhu)001:1038: sri can ch+gee mo badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah zhes brgya rtsa dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1039: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK081(zhu)001:1040: snying ga nas lcags kyu drangs la /
NK081(zhu)001:1041: bdag gi drung du bka' sdod par bsams la /
NK081(zhu)001:1042: de nas gtor ma 'bru gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK081(zhu)001:1043: a che ge mo pra ti b+ha ling+ta /
NK081(zhu)001:1044: pri b+ha ling+ta kha kha kh+aa hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK081(zhu)001:1046: sri can gyi sbubs 'jug gi gzugs gang yin pa des zos pas tshim zhing dga' ba dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1047: bdag gi bka' nyan par bsams la /
NK081(zhu)001:1049: sri can khyod rnams rnal 'byor bka' nyon cig /deng
NK081(zhu)001:1050: phyin chad sbubs 'jug gi sprul pa dor cig bsam
NK081(zhu)001:1051: pa ngan dang sbyor ba rtsub mo thams cad dor
NK081(zhu)001:1052: zhig /bsam pa byang chub kyi sems bskyed cig /de
NK081(zhu)001:1053: ltar ma byas na rdo rje 'chang gi bka' khyed
NK081(zhu)001:1054: kyi mgo dang snying 'gas par 'gyur ro //
NK081(zhu)001:1055: de bas khyed las ngan pa 'di rnams dran par
NK081(zhu)001:1056: gyis la sbubs 'jug gi sprul pa'i sems dor cig
NK081(zhu)001:1057: /de ring phan chad gnas 'dir las ngan pa'i bsam
NK081(zhu)001:1058: pa ma byed cig /de ltar nyan na gtor ma
NK081(zhu)001:1059: 'di khyod kyis 'dod yon lngar gyur nas mtho ris
NK081(zhu)001:1061: karma shan ting ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK081(zhu)001:1065: khro bo dpag tu med pa 'phros te gling gzhan du bskyal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:1066: ji ltar sri can yun ring chags pa yin yang /
NK081(zhu)001:1067: lan gsum byas na nges par 'dor bar 'gyur ro //
NK081(zhu)001:1069: slob dpon pad+mas bsam yas su ngam rta ra klung
NK081(zhu)001:1070: gong nag po'i sbubs bshig pa la mdzad pa rdzogs
NK081(zhu)001:1071: so ////mchod rten gdab pa rus chog gi lung phran
NK081(zhu)001:1073: a yu ga t+aa ra te he ru tsa ti ka a ti ka rak+sha tra ka n+aa ma /
NK081(zhu)001:1075: tshe 'das kyi don du mchod rten gdab pa'i rus chog lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:1076: bcom ldan 'das sgrol byed rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:1078: gang zhig tshe 'phos don bya'i phyir //
NK081(zhu)001:1079: rnal 'byor thugs rje'i sems ldan pas //
NK081(zhu)001:1080: sngon du bya ba kun byas te //
NK081(zhu)001:1081: bdag nyid las kyi lhar bskyed nas //
NK081(zhu)001:1082: gshed dbral shes pa bkug nas ni //
NK081(zhu)001:1083: khrus bya rtog sbyang sgrib pa dral //
NK081(zhu)001:1084: lhar bskyed dbang skur gnas ngan bsgral //
NK081(zhu)001:1085: chos skur bzhengs la mchod sogs sbyar //
NK081(zhu)001:1086: log non phan yon shes par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1087: snying rje ldan pas sems bskyed nas //
NK081(zhu)001:1089: tshe 'phos gang yin pa bsregs sbyangs pa'i rus pa dang thal ba la /
NK081(zhu)001:1090: cho ga dang mchod rten bya ste /
NK081(zhu)001:1096: de nas mi rtog pa'i ngang las lhar bskyed /
NK081(zhu)001:1097: de nas bden pa bdar zhing /
NK081(zhu)001:1098: drag po'i rdzas dang sngags pho nyas khro bo'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pas /
NK081(zhu)001:1099: phyogs bcu'i bdud bgegs dregs pa thams cad btul zhing /
NK081(zhu)001:1100: tshe 'das kyi shes pa srog gcod kyi bdud lha
NK081(zhu)001:1101: srin sde brgyad la sogs pa gang gi lag na
NK081(zhu)001:1102: gnas pa de nas rang dbang med par bkug par
NK081(zhu)001:1103: bsam zhing / a su n+ri tri pre du dzah
NK081(zhu)001:1104: r+n+ri badz+ra am gu sha dza dza zhes pas bstims
NK081(zhu)001:1105: bsam zhing / la / gson po'i lus bzhin gnas pa bsgoms /
NK081(zhu)001:1106: de nas bum chus tshig dang ldan pas bkru zhing /
NK081(zhu)001:1107: las kyi sgrib pa rnal 'byor sbyang ba dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1109: dpal na rag nas gsungs pa'i sngags kyis brabs pas /
NK081(zhu)001:1110: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma thams cad dag par bsam /
NK081(zhu)001:1111: sdig sgrib dang nyes ltung nyams chags thams cad yongs su dag par gyur cig /ces brjod /
NK081(zhu)001:1112: de nas yungs dkar dang bye ma la /
NK081(zhu)001:1113: ngan song sgo gcod kyi sngags bzlas pas /
NK081(zhu)001:1114: las dang nyon mongs pa drug gi rtogs pa ngan pa sbyangs shing /
NK081(zhu)001:1115: 'gro drug gi gnas ngan par skye ba'i sgo dgag go //
NK081(zhu)001:1116: de nas ring lngar bskyed pa'i 'phro 'dus /
NK081(zhu)001:1118: badz+ra b+han+d+ha ta tha sa sgrib pa dbral lo //
NK081(zhu)001:1121: thugs phyag mtshan sku yongs su rdzogs par bskyed /
NK081(zhu)001:1122: sku gsung thugs kyi lha dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1124: badz+ra ka ba tsa rak+sha h'u gis rdo rje cho ga dang ldan par bya'o //
NK081(zhu)001:1125: de nas ngan song las rgyal ba dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1126: khams gsum du phyir mi ldog par dbang bskur ro //
NK081(zhu)001:1127: de nas a las zla ba'i gdan thog tu bzhag
NK081(zhu)001:1128: yam las rlung gi bteg ste bar snang la bzhag
NK081(zhu)001:1129: go // de nas yi dam gyi lha yi snying po dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1130: ngan song sbyong ba'i sngags kyis btul thal brdungs la /
NK081(zhu)001:1131: yang dag pa'i sa la bsgral zhing sdig sgrib thams cad byang zhing bcom par bsgom mo //
NK081(zhu)001:1132: rus chog rdzogs so ////de nas mchod rten gdab pa ni /
NK081(zhu)001:1133: rus thal dang 'jim pa bsreg te /
NK081(zhu)001:1134: byin rlabs gzhan dang mthun par bya /
NK081(zhu)001:1135: 'bi 'bi byed pa nas 'debs pa'i dus su tshe
NK081(zhu)001:1136: 'das gong du lhar bskyed nas bar snang gi zla
NK081(zhu)001:1137: dal bzhugs pa de mchod rten gyi nang gi lhar
NK081(zhu)001:1138: bskyed de / nang rin po che'i gzhal yas khang
NK081(zhu)001:1139: la phyi mchod rten chos kyi sku yi gzugs brnyan
NK081(zhu)001:1140: la 'jig rten lha chen brgyad kyis bskor nas mchod
NK081(zhu)001:1141: pa byed par bsam zhing gdab /
NK081(zhu)001:1142: yi dam gyi snying po dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1143: ngan song sbyong ba'i sgo gcod kyi sngags brjod cing btab pas /
NK081(zhu)001:1145: khams gsum gyi sems can dang tshe 'das pa'i snying
NK081(zhu)001:1146: la rigs drug gi sa bon yod pa bsregs nas
NK081(zhu)001:1147: bsgribs pa dang / sems kyi chos nyid mngon du byas te /
NK081(zhu)001:1148: yi dam gyi lha'i sku phyag rgya chen po thob par bsgom mo //
NK081(zhu)001:1149: de nas chos skur byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK081(zhu)001:1151: de la pu tsa dbul ba'i rim pa rnams gzhung gzhan dang mthun par shes so //
NK081(zhu)001:1152: de nas gnyis pa log non ni //
NK081(zhu)001:1153: gshin gyi skegs dbud pa zhes bya ste /
NK081(zhu)001:1154: des kyang ma phan na gong gi de gshegs gsol byas la /
NK081(zhu)001:1155: mgo dang barla'i rus pa la s+aats+tsha re btab la /
NK081(zhu)001:1156: tshon dkar po dang nag po steng 'og tu zhabs sprad de /
NK081(zhu)001:1157: ma them 'og tu gru gsum brus la der bzhag go //
NK081(zhu)001:1158: des shi kha chod cing 'dre rgyun chad do //
NK081(zhu)001:1159: de nas spyi yi phan yon ni /
NK081(zhu)001:1160: rgyud sde las bsam gyis mi khyab pa bshad pas der blta bar bya'o //
NK081(zhu)001:1161: mchod rten gdab pa rus chog lung phran zhes bya ba /
NK081(zhu)001:1162: slob dpon bi ma la mi tra'i zhal snga nas
NK081(zhu)001:1163: gsungs pa zhang drung gnyags dz+ny+aa nas dkar chag tu
NK081(zhu)001:1164: btab pa rdzogs so ////ro sreg las kyi phreng ba
NK081(zhu)001:1166: bcom ldan 'das thugs rjes 'dren par byed pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK081(zhu)001:1167: sgyu 'phrul chen po'i rgyud sde las //
NK081(zhu)001:1168: rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba bsreg pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1169: gdos bcas thugs rjes sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK081(zhu)001:1170: ro bsreg las kyi phreng ba brtsams //
NK081(zhu)001:1171: rtag pa'i d+r+wa ba bsal nas ni //
NK081(zhu)001:1172: sku lnga lhun gyis grub par shog /dang por de nyid lus gzhag la //
NK081(zhu)001:1173: bgegs bskrad pa dang bca' ba dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1174: gdags dang sbyang dang dbang bskur dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1175: thab khung bsreg khang slob dpon dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1176: las gzhung sbyin sreg bsdu ba ste //
NK081(zhu)001:1177: lnga gnyis gcig gis don rdzogs pas //
NK081(zhu)001:1178: mdor bsdus spyi yi sdom du 'dod //
NK081(zhu)001:1179: de dag rgyas par bshad pa ni //
NK081(zhu)001:1180: ci nus sa yis rnam par dbye //
NK081(zhu)001:1181: e ram kham gsum ma lus kun //
NK081(zhu)001:1183: khog bsrung lhan cig skyes sogs la //
NK081(zhu)001:1184: brdeg dang bsnun dang gzhom pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1185: phrogs te brten pa gnyis med bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1186: bsrung ba'i 'khor lo'i cho ga yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1187: dam tshig sems dpa' bsrungs te bzhag /de ltar grangs dang zhag dus su //
NK081(zhu)001:1188: yang nas yang du bzla ste bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1189: khrus dang rgyan dang byug pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1190: phyi dang nang gi lnga gnyis la //
NK081(zhu)001:1191: brgya pa gnyis dang dag pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1192: chu la lan grangs mang bzlas te //
NK081(zhu)001:1193: rten mchog de la bkru bar bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1194: mi 'ching bcu phyed spos mar dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1195: dri yis de la yang dag byug /zhu chen khu bas btsos pa yi //
NK081(zhu)001:1196: ras kyis rten la yang dag dkri //
NK081(zhu)001:1197: spos mar thor cog de la bskon //
NK081(zhu)001:1198: mgul der rgyan yang gdags par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1199: phung po lnga yi gnas dag tu //
NK081(zhu)001:1200: rgyal ba lnga yi phyag rgya dgod //
NK081(zhu)001:1201: rtsa ru yum gyi phyag rgya dgod //
NK081(zhu)001:1202: dbang po rnam shes yul rnams su //
NK081(zhu)001:1203: sems dpa' sems ma 'joms pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1204: 'joms ma rim par dgod do zhes //
NK081(zhu)001:1205: rngam pa'i rgyud las gsungs pa yin //
NK081(zhu)001:1206: rgyud drug 'khor ba'i gnas rnams su //
NK081(zhu)001:1207: thub drug sa bon dgod pa yin //
NK081(zhu)001:1208: kun bzang yab yum de bzhin te //
NK081(zhu)001:1209: sdong bu re la lha rnams kyi //
NK081(zhu)001:1210: ma nor rtsa ba'i snying po dag /ras chen rgyu las byas te gdags //
NK081(zhu)001:1211: mya ngan 'das par gsungs pa yin //
NK081(zhu)001:1212: ro yi phyi rol shun pa la //
NK081(zhu)001:1213: 'gro drug sa bon bkod nas ni //
NK081(zhu)001:1215: rim gyis sbyang ba'i las su bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1216: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1217: rdo rje dril bu la sogs pa //
NK081(zhu)001:1218: dbang mchog byin la stegs la bzhag /de nas me thab brtsam bya ba //
NK081(zhu)001:1219: khru bzhi de yi tshad byas la //
NK081(zhu)001:1220: thur du brus te dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK081(zhu)001:1221: za byed dkyil 'khor phyag rgya dgod //
NK081(zhu)001:1222: rdo rje me yis mtshan pa de //
NK081(zhu)001:1223: thab khung yin par gsal bar gsungs //
NK081(zhu)001:1224: phyi rol ka ba bzhi btsugs la //
NK081(zhu)001:1225: 'og ma bgrangs sab sum brtseg bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1226: bar pa shig gis bardzanga dbus su //
NK081(zhu)001:1228: khro ba brgyad kyi snying po dgod //
NK081(zhu)001:1229: dbus su me yi sa bon dgod //
NK081(zhu)001:1230: bzhin phyogs shar du bstan te bzhag /ro la gzungs thag btags nas ni //
NK081(zhu)001:1231: glo skar bzhi nas drangs byas la //
NK081(zhu)001:1232: bla ma bzhi yi phyag tu phul //
NK081(zhu)001:1233: sum brtsegs yang thog chen po de //
NK081(zhu)001:1234: ras sam gro ga shing shun la //
NK081(zhu)001:1235: thugs rje'i dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK081(zhu)001:1236: lding bu bcas te gdags par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1237: de nas rdo rje rgyal po yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1239: rdo rje karma las mkhan gyis //
NK081(zhu)001:1240: bsrung dang bskrad pa'i las brtsams te //
NK081(zhu)001:1241: las kyi phreng ba rdzogs par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1242: rdo rje rgyal thebs bla ma yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1243: mtshams med lnga dang nye ba lnga //
NK081(zhu)001:1244: lci bzhi log brgyad la sogs pa //
NK081(zhu)001:1245: ro yi nyes pa bgrang zhing bshags //
NK081(zhu)001:1246: rdo rje skabs sbyor bla ma yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1247: skabs skabs kun tu mchod pa dbul //
NK081(zhu)001:1248: bkra shis gnas kyi smon lam gdab //
NK081(zhu)001:1249: skabs sam kun gyi mjug tu gdab //
NK081(zhu)001:1250: rdo rje grangs kyi ltangs 'dzin pas //
NK081(zhu)001:1251: grangs bzug dkar byang bla mar dbul //
NK081(zhu)001:1252: sdig pa'i gnag byang bshags shing bsreg /bzlas brjod 'phro 'dus rtog tshogs rnams //
NK081(zhu)001:1253: sbyang te rang rang lha ru brlab //
NK081(zhu)001:1254: tshogs dang po byed mchod pa kun //
NK081(zhu)001:1255: rim par mdun du brlabs byas la //
NK081(zhu)001:1256: de las ra skyes ram las me //
NK081(zhu)001:1257: bskyed de rang bzhin spyan drangs bstim //
NK081(zhu)001:1258: a li u li ta pa yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1259: tshogs kyi mchod pa skabs su bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1260: mchod dang bstod pa'i rim pa bzhin //
NK081(zhu)001:1261: me lha'i lto bar gzhal yas khang //
NK081(zhu)001:1262: lha dang bcas pa rim par bskyed //
NK081(zhu)001:1263: gong gi dkyil 'khor gsal btab la //
NK081(zhu)001:1264: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs te //
NK081(zhu)001:1265: gnyis su med par bstim par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1266: mchod pa'i rim pa gong bzhin phul //
NK081(zhu)001:1267: bstod pa la sogs de dang mtshungs //
NK081(zhu)001:1268: me yi ltas dang bzang dang ngan //
NK081(zhu)001:1269: rim pa bzhin du brtag par bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1270: de nas rdo rje bsdu ba yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1271: rim pa bzhin du bsdus byas la //
NK081(zhu)001:1272: dam pa yin na sku gdung yang //
NK081(zhu)001:1273: lhag ma bsdus te mchod rten nam //
NK081(zhu)001:1274: sku'am gtsug lag zhal zhal lam //
NK081(zhu)001:1275: thang ka'i ri mo bya ba 'am //
NK081(zhu)001:1276: rdzas dang bsres la ril bu bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1277: sbyin sreg bya bar mkhas pas bshad //
NK081(zhu)001:1278: de nas bsdu dang bshags pa dang //
NK081(zhu)001:1279: gshegs su gsol ba rim bzhin bya //
NK081(zhu)001:1280: tshon rtsi bsdus te rol mo yis //
NK081(zhu)001:1281: rgya mtsho chen por bskyal te btang //
NK081(zhu)001:1282: 'khor ba'i sems can log par 'khrul ba shin tu nyon mongs dang bcas pa /
NK081(zhu)001:1283: dral zhing bsreg phyir gdos bcas sbyang phyir dri med bshes gnyen gdung ba bdag gis kyang /
NK081(zhu)001:1284: sgyu 'phrul rgyu mtsho rtogs dka' rngam pa mtha' yas rgyud chen las btus pa'i /
NK081(zhu)001:1285: rgya mtsho sems can rtog bcas 'di kun zag med shog //
